divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking pictures of unique cloud formations in my backyard. They looked like effects of chemtrails with some areas having a "oil" sheen affect on them. I took perhaps 20 pictures and downloaded them to the computer. I slightly balanced levels on the photo and they were easily visible, though without the balancing they were more difficult to make out, though easily seen. I did not notice them while taking the pictures.
